Using ChatGPT to Re-Purpose Your Podcast Content
text:
Hey there,

My name is Tiago and I have been indie-building products for almost two years now.

I have played around with a lot of products and my most recent one uses ChatGPT API.

It's called PodSqueeze and helps podcasters repurpose their content by creating show notes, newsletters, mentions, tweets, etc...

I am a podcaster myself and think that this idea has great potential, but at the same time the competition is increasing a lot.

Would love to have your feedback. Do you find podsqueeze valuable?

Thanks
